## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="fb9e5-355">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder>物件，並附加文字字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fb9e5-355">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> object and appends text strings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fb9e5-356">此範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.StartStyle%2A>方法，以指定緩慢的說話速率字串加入，其中會列舉順序的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fb9e5-356">The example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.StartStyle%2A> method to specify a slow speaking rate for the string being added, which enumerates the contents of an order.</span></span>  
  
